   <TD>*<SPACER TYPE=HORIZONTAL SIZE=6></TD>
   <TD>Instead of the <i>line_nums</i> parameter, you can
       <INPUT TYPE=submit value='set a cookie to turn $new_linenum'>
       line numbers.</TD>
